                        <p>No, our PDF merger preserves the original quality of your documents. The merged PDF will maintain the same resolution and quality as your original files.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Are my files secure when using this tool?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down faq-toggle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <div class="faq-answer-content">
                        <p>Yes, all file processing happens directly in your browser. Your PDFs are never uploaded to our servers, ensuring complete privacy and security.</p>
                    </div>
