                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down faq-toggle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <div class="faq-answer-content">
                        <p>Yes, simply select "Custom Order" from the Page Order dropdown and drag the files into your preferred sequence before merging.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
            
            <div class="faq-item">
                <div class="faq-question">
                    <span>Is this service really free?</span>
                    <i class="fas fa-chevron-down faq-toggle"></i>
                </div>
                <div class="faq-answer">
                    <div class="faq-answer-content">
                        <p>Yes, our PDF merger is completely free to use with no hidden charges. We may display ads to support the service, but there are no fees for merging your files.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
